      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, smooth journey without the brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and it's ready to hit the road with its next owner today! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
