    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E92 M3 featuring the celebrated S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and new throttle valve actuators, ensuring the 8,400 RPM redline is explored with confidence. The chassis retains its composure via the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system, and the M Variable Differential Lock delivers precise power distribution during high-lateral-G cornering. The induction note from the individual throttle bodies remains crisp and unfettered. While the exterior shows minor stone peppering consistent with spirited road use, the subframe and VANOS system are in excellent health. A purist-spec machine optimized for turn-in response and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 34500.0,
